<template>
  <section class="members">
    <tab-content-grid
      :showSearch="true"
      btnSecondary="Invite members"
      btnPrimary="Delete members"
      title="Members"
      @handleSecondaryBtn="handleModalOpen(communityModalTypes.addMembers)"
      @handlePrimaryBtn="handleModalOpen(communityModalTypes.deleteMembers)"
    >
      <template v-if="groups">
        <group-component
          :image="member.alias.image"
          :name="member.alias.name"
          activityName="Commented your post:"
          date="01-24-2019, 07:21"
          :bottomText="member.text"
          v-for="member in groups.members"
          :key="member.id"
          :userHasEditPermissions="data.userHasEditPermissions"
        />
      </template>
    </tab-content-grid>
  </section>
</template>

<script>
import {
  communityModalTypes,
  communityAreas,
  getMembers
} from '@/services/community.service';
import GroupComponent from '@/components/Blog/GroupComponent';
import TabContentGrid from '../common/TabContentGrid';

export default {
  name: communityAreas.members,
  components: {
    GroupComponent,
    TabContentGrid
  },
  props: {
    data: {
      type: Object,
      required: true
    },
    communityId: {
      type: String,
      required: true
    }
  },
  data() {
    return {
      communityModalTypes,
      /*@TODO revise*/
      groups: null
    };
  },
  methods: {
    handleModalOpen(modalType) {
      this.$emit('openModal', modalType);
    },
    async getData() {
      this.groups = await getMembers(this.communityId, 1);
    }
  },
  async mounted() {
    await this.getData();
  }
};
</script>
<style lang="scss" scoped></style>
